OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FThe day will start with bright
OL,6,Fspells and the odd rather blustery
OL,7,Fshower. It should become fine during
OL,8,Fthe morning, though thicker cloud and
OL,9,Fsome rain will arrive from the
OL,10,Fsouthwest heading into the afternoon.
OL,11,FMild, though remaining breezy.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FIt will be a cloudy, damp and
OL,14,Fin places murky evening, with fog
OL,15,Fpatches on the hills. Turning drier
OL,16,Fovernight, though staying rather
OL,17,Fcloudy. Mild, and fairly breezy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
