OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FTuesday will be a mostly dry,
OL,6,Fthough often fairly cloudy and breezy
OL,7,Fday. Some bright spells developing,
OL,8,Fespecially in the afternoon, when it
OL,9,Fwill become very mild.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,12,FWednesday looks mostly dry and very
OL,13,Fmild with some sunshine, especially in
OL,14,Fthe east. Cooling down thereafter and
OL,15,Fturning more unsettled with some rain
OL,16,Fand strong winds possible at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
